juniDnsAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the DNS component of the SNMP agent in the Juniper E-series family of products.

juniDnsAgentV1.name: juniDnsAgentV1
juniDnsAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the DNS component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This version
        of the DNS component was supported in JUNOSe 3.0 thru 5.1 system
        releases.
juniDnsAgentV1.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the DNS application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when IPv6 address support was added.

juniDnsAgentV2.name: juniDnsAgentV2
juniDnsAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the DNS component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This version
        of the DNS component is supported in JUNOSe 5.2 and subsequent system
        releases.
juniDnsAgentV2.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the DNS application in JUNOSe.
